headline: American Outdoor Brands, Inc. (AOUT) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: American Outdoor Brands (AOUT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +750.00% and +28.78%, respectively, for the quarter ended April 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
